{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01K9f4gfvjcJUqviKtSoLPfF","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me plan and implement the GAME_SETTLED handler. This is a complex task with multiple components:\n\n1. Create the handler file with DB helpers and orchestration logic\n2. Register it in index.ts\n3. Write integration tests\n4. Add necessary tables to TRUNCATE list in tests\n\nLet me create the handler file first.\n\nThe handler needs to:\n1. Parse the `game.settled` payload\n2. For each player:\n   a. Check `questEligible(player)` — skip if refund\n   b. Load active assignments with challenge data (JOIN)\n   c. Run the adapter for each assignment, and if progression should happen, insert a progress event, increment the counter, and check if the assignment is complete\n   d. When an assignment completes, emit the appropriate reward intent (either points or crate)\n   e. Grant wager points with the round ID as the source\n   f. Trigger crate drops tied to the game settlement event\n3. Emit the reward pool funding once per round\n4. Wrap each player's processing in try/catch for error isolation\n\nLet me write it now.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2684,"cache_read_input_tokens":71981,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2684},"output_tokens":27,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a0816eb3-ec81-48b4-9f7e-e95cff86009e","uuid":"7da42146-f6f7-4623-bc42-b1733d602ffc"}
